  <h2>About iWatched</h2>
  <p>iWatched helps you keep a personal log of the movies and shows you’ve watched. Mark titles as watched, save items to revisit later, and favourite the ones you love.</p>

  <h3>What you can do</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Track watched movies and shows</li>
    <li>Save titles to a “Saved” list for later</li>
    <li>Favourite titles you love</li>
    <li>Search and browse quickly</li>
    <li>Create a shareable profile with a custom URL and visibility controls</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>How it works</h3>
  <p>Search for a title, open its page, and add it to your watched, saved, or favourites with one click. Your activity appears on your profile depending on your visibility settings.</p>

  <h3>Data & attribution</h3>
  <p>Posters and metadata are provided by The Movie Database (TMDb). This product uses the TMDb API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDb.</p>

  <h3>Privacy</h3>
  <p>Your profile visibility can be set to Public, Friends, or Private. You can edit or remove entries at any time. See our <a href="/policy/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="/policy/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>.</p>

  <h3>What’s next</h3>
  <p>Planned improvements include OAuth login, richer stats, and import/export tools.</p>
